title: 12/10/20 HOUR 2- Pat Forde and Tony Dungy
itunes:title: 12/10/20 HOUR 2- Pat Forde and Tony Dungy
description:
Pat Forde tells Dan all the teams in college football that are getting a raw deal with the football playoff and the way they are ranked. Tony Dungy tells Dan that this is probably the first time we have ever seen the Dallas Cowboys being flexed out of.
